00:19:47.900 --> 00:19:51.240
We can accelerate that process
and we get an old mouse,

00:19:51.240 --> 00:19:54.720
50% older, and it has
this bent spine kyphosis.

00:19:54.720 --> 00:19:56.880
it has gray hair, it's organs are old.

