01:27:39.410 --> 01:27:40.760
The second is that there

01:27:40.760 --> 01:27:44.410
is what's called xenohormetic
molecules in plants.

01:27:44.410 --> 01:27:47.010
That term, xenohormesis is a term

01:27:47.010 --> 01:27:50.220
